content: Without stable membranes provided with channels operated by proteins, there would be no cells. But without cells, there would be no proteins that could form the membrane channels.
translations: ita:Senza membrane stabili dotate di canali operati da proteine, non ci sarebbero cellule. Ma senza cellule, non ci sarebber
